@startuml
title UML sequence behaviour — Live media relayed without recording
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam ArrowColor #344054
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #344054
  FontColor #101828
}
skinparam package {
  BorderColor #667085
  FontColor #101828
  BackgroundColor #F9FAFB
}
actor "Host" as host
box "Frontend — Prayer client" #E0F2FE
  participant "Setup / Green room" as setup
  participant "RoomTransport" as transport
end box
box "Backend — Room origin" #D1FADF
  participant "Room origin" as origin
  participant "Room registry" as registry
end box

host -> setup : Open host setup
setup --> host : State that nothing is recorded (L2-071)
host -> transport : Publish live presence media
transport -> origin : Relay encoded frames (WebTransport / HTTP/3)
origin -> registry : Read ephemeral room state
registry --> origin : Room membership
origin -> origin : Fan out to subscribers without persisting (L2-071)
origin --> transport : Relayed; no server-side recording or archival (L2-071)
note over origin, registry : The Room origin holds only ephemeral room state; no VOD or recording capability exists in v1 (L2-071)
@enduml
